  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "Active GPS Antenna",
      "text": "The MikroTik ACGPSA is a standalone active GPS antenna designed to operate in the 1575.4 MHz spectrum. It delivers reliable and accurate positioning data for your MikroTik LtAP or LtAP mini devices. With compact dimensions of 46.5 × 26.5 × 12.5 mm, the antenna is suitable for a wide range of deployment scenarios. Its active design ensures stable GPS signal reception, which is ideal for mobile, IoT, or vehicular setups where precise timing and location information are required."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Active GPS Antenna",
      "text": "The ACGPSA is rated IP67, making it resistant to dust and water ingress, perfect for outdoor use. It comes with an internal magnet and double-sided tape, allowing it to be securely attached to metal or flat surfaces. A long 5-meter cable with SMA male connector enables flexible installation. To connect with LtAP devices, the ACSMAUFL pigtail is required (sold separately), providing a convenient and secure link between antenna and router."
    }
  ],
